fields.description:
Tokyo tower and Tokyo sky tree··· 

 Fuji Mountain and Sakura in full bloom··· 

 all romantic sceneries that you experience at Tokyo in a floral spring day are incorporated in this exclusive limited edition cleansing oil. 

 for combination to oily skin conditions

the first step for “pore-less skin”

a lightweight cleansing oil that leaves the skin clean, fresh and refined.

wash away pore concerns-enlarged pores and clogged pores that lead to blackheads with our innovative natural origin system for superb cleansing. effectively remove make-up and impurities inside pores while maintaining the skin’s necessary moisture level. empowered with sakura complex, this cleansing oil minimizes pores by eliminating excess sebum and visibly smoothes the skin’s surface. 

ideal for normal to oily skin types and acne-prone skin.
fields.name: fresh pore clarifying gentle cleansing oil travel collection limited edition

fields.description:
The #1 cleansing oil legacy started with Unmask, our first magic oil since 1967. today, through half a century of continuous innovation, its superior performance has captured the trust of women from around the world.

In 2013, shu uemura goes back to its origin. the legendary Unmask is re-expressed in a modern touch, creating a range of limited edition cleansing oils.

for all skin conditions - Camellias embody the elegance of Unmask’s origins. Infused with Asian Botanical Oils such as Camellia Oil and Ginger Root Oil, this formula cleanses with gentle touch and maintains skin’s moisture balance. Leaves skin feeling comfortable with a fresh and sensuous rosemary aroma.
fields.name: high performance balancing cleansing oil advanced formula unmask edition

fields.description:
the prelude to a beauty dream begins by adding an alluring tint to lips, the ultimate symbol of femininity. a combination of nudey pastel colors in 2 dreamy limited edition shades are offered.

bright pink shade: the supreme matte pink will turn heads, and ignite your deepest desires.

light beige shade: say it with texture with this barely there, supreme matte nude lips to highlight a glowing beauty canvas.
fields.name: rouge unlimited supreme matte blossom dream (limited edition)

fields.description:
the rebirth of gloss unlimited

 this new shape memorizing lip gloss is designed to create unlimited mirror shine with “3D shape-memory technology” to give lips a high shine veil that maintain voluminous shine. the new applicator traps gloss inside the circle and slant oval shaped applicator fits perfectly with the lip shape to achiever precise application in one stroke by gradually evening out the gloss on your lips providing a new and sophisticated gloss experience.

the comfortable, light texture melts into lips through a moisture active complex formula that includes a new lotus flower extract nourishes and protect fragile lips and a special rich blend of botanical oils for moisture comfort. lips feel moisturized all day long.
fields.name: gloss unlimited limited edition

fields.description:
re-discover the joy of shu uemura’s professional atelier of color with three new special edition matte textured refills in charming pastel shades in a refillable quad custom case.

now everyone can easily achieve pro-level make-up gradation, color payoff, and ultra-smooth matte texture. 

“matte texture gives a more soothing, warm, and soft impression than pearl or glitter textures. even when exposed to a strong light, matte texture maintains its true color. pale, soft, and warm colors are best suited to matte textures.” 

a variety of fresh pastel greens- light minty tint of spring green and bright grassy green that evoke the ripe fields of spring. not pop, but an active, energetic femininity.
fields.name: unmask palette green

fields.description:
dreamy lashes maximize your colorful make-up fantasy festivities.

dramatize your look with fluffy, colorful feathers or accentuate your eyes with feather-light lashes!

a rainbow of colored feathers graphically accented by black lash hair.

“feather adds new textures for even richer make-up expression. these are to add a sense of fun and playfulness, liberate your mind. I designed them to create a colorful and soft impression. bending the band a little will make them softer and easier to apply and wear. ” Yuki Asano, International Make-up Director.
fields.name: rainbow feather S false eyelashes

fields.description:
exotic skyscrapers with Shanghai tower… 

thousands of star are shining above…

with this exclusive limited edition cleansing oil, all memories of your sparkling days in Shanghai come dazzling again.
 
for dull skin complexion, removing melanin-filled dead cells is the first step in brightening care. fortified with the ultimate removal system, our latest development, the lightly textured formula effectively removes accumulated melanin and heavy make-up.

empowered with our advanced brightening technology this brightening cleansing oil contains an innovative combination of mito-white complex and vitamin c to help prevent the accumulation of melanin deep within. day-after-day, the skin looks clarified and brightened with an even-toned complexion.
fields.name: whitefficient clear brightening gentle cleansing oil travel collection limited ed.
